author: @Beckford4000
content: As a gay man, I utterly hate being referred to as a "queen". Don't apply such terms to people until you are sure they are OK with it. You have no idea what that newsreader prefers, so don't call him a "queen" because you're creating stereotypes about an entire group of people.
